  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/2a754ab31bc979873536dfa08aa5ef46.poster.avif?t=1751277645\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/2a754ab31bc979873536dfa08aa5ef46.webm?t=1751277645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/2a754ab31bc979873536dfa08aa5ef46.mp4?t=1751277645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The road to madness starts here</strong></h2>Play as an alchemist and metaphysician who meddled with dark forces one time too many. Dragged into an infinite abyss of madness and monsters. How will he escape?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You are in Control</strong></h2>Doge, roll, dash, wall jump, flip, while simultaneously shooting. Madshot: Road to madness offers fluid and responsive movement, you’re always in control of the mayhem.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/98e4b85be57cf37226d972109cec5b7c.poster.avif?t=1751277645\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/98e4b85be57cf37226d972109cec5b7c.webm?t=1751277645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/98e4b85be57cf37226d972109cec5b7c.mp4?t=1751277645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless hordes</strong></h2>Slaughter, Subdue and control endless hordes of enemies. Get the highest score possible, challenge your friends or climb the online leaderboards. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/6276ed813fe1546199aa66a26cacd562.poster.avif?t=1751277645\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/6276ed813fe1546199aa66a26cacd562.webm?t=1751277645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/6276ed813fe1546199aa66a26cacd562.mp4?t=1751277645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create lethal combinations</strong></h2>There's a big focus on synergies between unlockable weapons, sidearms, upgrades, and ultimate abilities. Discovering the right combinations will be vital.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/cf677fcfa10cfc907e994a4707d340f9.poster.avif?t=1751277645\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/cf677fcfa10cfc907e994a4707d340f9.webm?t=1751277645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/cf677fcfa10cfc907e994a4707d340f9.mp4?t=1751277645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/2a754ab31bc979873536dfa08aa5ef46.poster.avif?t=1751277645\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/2a754ab31bc979873536dfa08aa5ef46.webm?t=1751277645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/2a754ab31bc979873536dfa08aa5ef46.mp4?t=1751277645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The road to madness starts here</strong></h2>Play as an alchemist and metaphysician who meddled with dark forces one time too many. Dragged into an infinite abyss of madness and monsters. How will he escape?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You are in Control</strong></h2>Doge, roll, dash, wall jump, flip, while simultaneously shooting. Madshot: Road to madness offers fluid and responsive movement, you’re always in control of the mayhem.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/98e4b85be57cf37226d972109cec5b7c.poster.avif?t=1751277645\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/98e4b85be57cf37226d972109cec5b7c.webm?t=1751277645\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2149610/extras/98e4b85be57cf37226d972109cec5b7c.mp4?t=1751277645\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless hordes</strong></h2>Slaughter, Subdue and control endless hordes of enemies. Get the highest score possible, challenge your friends or climb the online leaderboards. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay mu